Package moulton.scalable.containers

The containers package contains classes that are intended for holding menu components, especially panel classes which serve as nodes in the menu rendering tree structure.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Container
    The container of the menu.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ListPanel
    A subclass of VirtualPanel.
    MenuManager
    The menu manager will handle the rendering of its menu on a graphics object through MenuManager.render(Graphics).
    Panel
    A panel to serve as a parent component and backdrop for other MenuComponents.
    PartitionPanel
    PartitionPanel is a type of Panel with up to two partitions dividing up the space into four sectors: left, right, bottom, and top.
    VirtualPanel
    An improved Panel class that can be scrolled and can thus hold hidden elements in "virtual space".
